{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT processes the text into memory into as many summaries as desired.",
    "Then, a multiple-choice test with ten questions is given.",
    "ChatGPT answers these questions based on text input provided by the researcher.",
    "Finally, to ensure that the evaluation is homogeneous, the researcher created a summary assessment rubric according to two aspects, namely content and writing style, by modifying several assessment aspects that had been developed previously (Vázquez-Cano et al., 2023).",
    "The population of this study was N=1034 students from Universitas Negeri Makassar (UNM), Universitas Timor (Unimor, and Makassar Health Polytechnic (Poltekkes Makassar)."
  ]
}